<p>&#8216;The First-tier Tribunal (Charity) has dismissed the disqualification appeal from a former church pastor who was banned from being a charity trustee for ten years after the Charity Commission concluded, inter alia, that he had used charitable funds for foreign trips that did not appear to be for charitable purposes.&#8217;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.lawandreligionuk.com/2019/10/14/disqualifying-a-church-pastor-from-charity-trusteeship-phelps/">Full Story</a></p><p> Law &amp; Religion UK, 14th October 2019</p><p>Source: <a href="http://www.lawandreligionuk.com">www.lawandreligionuk.com</a></p>